                class="absolute left-0 bottom-0 w-full h-[2px] bg-secondary-600 scale-x-0 opacity-0 group-[.underline-active]:scale-x-100 group-[.underline-active]:opacity-100 transition-transform duration-500 delay-700 origin-left"
              ></span>
